{ Or  16.Na2  Nf6  17.Nb4  Ne7  18.Nxa6  c5  19.dxc6  Nxc6  , when the position is difficult to assess.  The a6-Knight is stranded, and Black has a strong central position and is well coordinated. It looks tough to play for White. We doubt that many human opponents would start this pawn raid with Na2-b4-a6, but it's a critical try for sure. }
